dev-workshop.dev.recipe.default.markdownDescription:
Define which recipe is used by `#dev-workshop.build#`. It also applies to auto build. Recipes are referred to by their names as defined in `#dev-workshop.dev.recipes#`. Note there are two particular values: 
- `first` means to use the first recipe in `#dev-workshop.dev.recipes#`;
- `lastUsed` means to use the last run recipe.
